{"tid":1147404,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"毒撚柒頭真係唔好坐巴士","createTime":"2019-05-09T23:30:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T01:17:19.000Z","uid":211405,"like":5,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c9d292bfa54ecbad5adc0fe816bcad756e56fd05","tid":1147404,"uid":211405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:30:50.000Z","msg":"我係一個普通上班族，但個身形就唔太普通，米9身高，80kg<br />\n<br />\n我每朝返工放工都會揀上層靠窗位坐(我上個位比較少人)<br />\n<br />\n隨著愈多愈多人上巴士，我個心就愈跳愈快，點解仲未有人坐我隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自問人緣幾好，坐果陣都盡量收埋對腳，屈住咁坐，費時過界。 <br />\n<br />\n但係每一次架車full 左，我隔離都會有個空位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都唔奢望有美腿OL坐我隔離，就連地盤佬瞄到我隔離個位都扮睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解？點解阿？地盤佬企左成日，成身臭汗味，竟然寧願落去企都唔坐我隔離？<br />\n<br />\n到底我做錯咩？我都係想做個正常人姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcc785e07d5b4cc88559bc653a41029230121d00","tid":1147404,"uid":201604,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:32:10.000Z","msg":"前面條友畀你頂撚死"},{"pid":"2d8fcb0f8168fda0d34f0c5b6e2376bc7cfb33eb","tid":1147404,"uid":18517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:33:39.000Z","msg":"有身型無樣都係死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67ee3efaa475d2b921f3586dc536e647c473a733","tid":1147404,"uid":211405,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bcc785e07d5b4cc88559bc653a41029230121d00","tid":1147404,"uid":201604,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:32:10.000Z","msg":"前面條友畀你頂撚死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:34:21.000Z","msg":"我就係想前面果個調過黎我隔離坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3713ad2ed13f56a6b7d08858d6b1e03b35fad524","tid":1147404,"uid":211405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:35:27.000Z","msg":"依家又自己坐緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好尷尬啊，想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ba4875ffcc37edc10a36f5c4f509b8ea7c0263","tid":1147404,"uid":234235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:38:47.000Z","msg":"得兩個可能<br />\n<br />\n太型棍霸氣側漏人地怕左<br />\n太柒毒人地驚左"},{"pid":"8c2cff37849616c91d7a1a4826df84079ba60c07","tid":1147404,"uid":211405,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2d8fcb0f8168fda0d34f0c5b6e2376bc7cfb33eb","tid":1147404,"uid":18517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:33:39.000Z","msg":"有身型無樣都係死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:40:46.000Z","msg":"珍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁高對我黎講係惡夢，好似一碌竹掛住個柒頭示眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 受盡恥笑<br />\n利申，小弟行旺角，聽到有人笑就好敏感，連行街都行到好唔開心，日日返屋企匿埋喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a6ca2235dc9ae2086cbd78109256565c42bd745","tid":1147404,"uid":211405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14ba4875ffcc37edc10a36f5c4f509b8ea7c0263","tid":1147404,"uid":234235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:38:47.000Z","msg":"得兩個可能<br />\n<br />\n太型棍霸氣側漏人地怕左<br />\n太柒毒人地驚左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:41:27.000Z","msg":"後者機會大啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ef65e61de078653c2af02c8ae39179ec426589","tid":1147404,"uid":56731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:42:27.000Z","msg":"臭"},{"pid":"dcea29029f9973e5a0153cbf76edec0efd2f7bbc","tid":1147404,"uid":211405,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:43:34.000Z","msg":"俾個正皮當可憐下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efaf99d52d6593271f95954e18cc8ebeabccca20","tid":1147404,"uid":11695,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"reply